from django.urls import path
from .views import (
    NotificationListView,
    UnreadNotificationsView,
    MarkNotificationAsReadView,
    SendNotificationView,
)

urlpatterns = [
    path("notifications/", NotificationListView.as_view(), name="notifications_list"),
    path("notifications/unread/", UnreadNotificationsView.as_view(), name="unread_notifications"),
    path("notifications/read/<int:pk>/", MarkNotificationAsReadView.as_view(), name="mark_as_read"),
    path("notifications/send/", SendNotificationView.as_view(), name="send_notification"),
]
